<p>Nothing should hit that code, but now we'll know if something does.</p>
<h2 id="reactivate-in-stripe">Reactivate in Stripe <a class="headerlink" href="reactivate-subscription#reactivate-in-stripe" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>To reactivate the Subscription, we first need to fetch it. In the Stripe API docs,
find "Retrieve a Subscription." Every object can be fetched using the same retrieve
method. Copy this. Then, add, <code>$subscription =</code> and paste. Replace the subscription
ID with <code>$user-&gt;getSubscription()-&gt;getStripeSubscriptionId()</code>:</p>
