<p>All of that will be reversed, and the subscription will be alive!</p>
<p>Let's do it! In <code>ProfileController</code>, add a <code>$stripeSubscription =</code> in front of the
<code>$stripeClient</code> call. Below that, use <code>$this-&gt;get('subscription_helper')-&gt;addSubscriptionToUser()</code>
and pass it <code>$stripeSubscription</code> and the current user:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="7d15244071">
